snippet.title: Coin Smith | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to Coin Smith, an addictive idle clicker game where your journey to unimaginable riches starts with a single tap. Set in a world inspired by the ancient Lydian Empire, the birthplace of coins, you'll build, upgrade, and strategize your way to wealth and glory.

Wishlist now on STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2528140/Coin_Smith/

Website : https://www.thepummel.com/

#coinsmith #steam #pcgaming #clickergame #idle
